# Implementation Plan - Fix Gallery Deletion Bug

The user reported that deleting a single image from the pre-upload gallery removes all of them. I will refactor the logic to use a more stable approach using a JavaScript array to manage the state.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> I will be switching the gallery management logic from direct `DataTransfer` manipulation to using a standard JavaScript array (`pendingFiles`). This avoids potential browser-specific quirks with clearing and re-adding items to a `DataTransferItemList`.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Robust Gallery State Management (All Admin Views)
#### [MODIFY] [packages/create.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/admin/packages/create.php)
#### [MODIFY] [packages/edit.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/admin/packages/edit.php)
#### [MODIFY] [excursions/create.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/admin/excursions/create.php)
#### [MODIFY] [excursions/edit.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/admin/excursions/edit.php)

- Replace the `accumulator` (`DataTransfer`) with a local `pendingFiles` array.
- Update `updateGalleryPreview` to:
    - Clear the preview grid.
    - Loop through `pendingFiles`.
    - Create a *fresh* `DataTransfer` object.
    - Append each file to the new `DataTransfer`.
    - Assign the new `DataTransfer.files` to the `input.files`.
    - Generate the preview cards.
- Update the deletion logic for *new* photos to simply `splice` from the `pendingFiles` array and call `updateGalleryPreview`.

### 2. Harmonize Existing Gallery Deletion (Edit Views)
#### [MODIFY] [packages/edit.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/admin/packages/edit.php)
#### [MODIFY] [excursions/edit.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/dominican_travel/app/views/admin/excursions/edit.php)

- Adopt the delegated event listener approach for *existing* photos (the one the user manually added to `excursions/edit.php`) to ensure consistency and prevent potential conflicts between scripts.

